40|$|AbstractSharp {{estimates}} for the <b>mean</b> <b>curvatures</b> of hypersurfaces in Riemannian manifolds are known from the works of Jorge-Xavier [3], Markvorsen [6] and Vlachos [11]. We first give a simplified proof of these estimates. This proof shows that a similar original result holds for hypersurfaces in Einstein manifolds which are warped product of ℝ by Ricci-flat manifolds...|$|R
